      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/kkr-said-to-mull-selling-stake-in-india-s-3-billion-jb-pharma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp; Co. 正在探索各种选择，包括出售其在印度 JB Chemicals &amp; Co. 的控股权。据知情人士透露，潜在买家对此感兴趣。]]></description>
