      <title>股息削减后 St. James's Place 股价跌幅自 2016 年以来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/st-james-s-place-plunges-most-since-2016-after-dividend-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在基金经理削减股息支出且盈利低于预期后，St. James’s Place Plc 的股价在伦敦遭遇七年多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
