    <item>
      <title>印度称红海袭击增加了中东贸易路线的紧迫性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/india-says-red-sea-attacks-add-urgency-to-mideast-trade-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度驻阿拉伯联合酋长国大使表示，红海局势的动荡增加了建立替代贸易走廊的必要性，以将货物从印度运往欧洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/india-says-red-sea-attacks-add-urgency-to-mideast-trade-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:54:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冯德莱恩警告欧洲必须加强威胁防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/europe-needs-to-ramp-up-defenses-to-threats-von-der-leyen-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩表示，乌克兰盟友应考虑利用俄罗斯冻结资产的利润为基辅购买武器，并警告欧洲必须为更广泛战争的风险做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/europe-needs-to-ramp-up-defenses-to-threats-von-der-leyen-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰勒·温佩 (Taylor Wimpey) 预计英国房屋销售将再次出现年度下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/taylor-wimpey-expects-another-drop-in-uk-home-sales-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的开发商之一预计今年将建造更少的房屋，这将给该国的住房短缺带来更大的压力，尽管人们对抵押贷款利率走软的乐观情绪有所增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/taylor-wimpey-expects-another-drop-in-uk-home-sales-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:10:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
